node.text:
Some new features to talk about:
New design with front screen (front facing display)
5K Video
Removable Lens
20 Megapixel Photos (upgraded from 12MP)
More Battery Life
In-Camera Horizon Leveling
HyperSmooth 3.0
#GoProHERO9
#MoreEverything
@gopro
@north_trampoline_official
